WEBVTT

00:10:58.551 --> 00:11:01.066
Fantastic people, so inspired.

00:11:01.066 --> 00:11:04.322
To look after Antarctica,

00:11:04.322 --> 00:11:10.658
you've got to first engage people
with this extraordinary place,

00:11:10.658 --> 00:11:14.858
form a relationship, form a bond,

00:11:14.858 --> 00:11:17.621
form some love.

00:11:17.621 --> 00:11:21.080
It is such a privilege
to go to Antarctica,

00:11:21.080 --> 00:11:22.427
I can't tell you.

00:11:22.427 --> 00:11:24.006
I feel so lucky,

00:11:24.006 --> 00:11:27.233
and I've been 35 times in my life,

00:11:27.233 --> 00:11:31.951
and all those people who come with us
return home as great champions,